<lb n="1068c05"/><head type="no">No. 2163</head><div1 type="xu">
<lb n="1068c06"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><jhead><note n="1068001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】鎌倉時代寫高山寺藏本，【甲】享保二年寫大谷大學藏本，【乙】大日本佛教全書，【丙】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，常曉和尚請來＝法琳寺常曉律師【甲】，〔常曉…錄〕八字－【丙】</note><note n="1068001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">【原】鎌倉時代寫高山寺藏本，【甲】享保二年寫大谷大學藏本，【乙】大日本佛教全書，【丙】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，〔常曉和尚請來目錄〕八字－【丙】，常曉和尚請來＝法琳寺常曉律師【甲】</note><app n="1068001"><lem>常曉和尚請來目錄</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">法琳寺常曉律師目錄</rdg></app><note n="1068001" place="foot" type="rest">【原】鎌倉時代寫高山寺藏本，【甲】享保二年寫大谷大學藏本，【乙】大日本佛教全書，【丙】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="1068c07"/>
<lb n="1068c08"/><mulu type="序" level="1" label="上表"/><p>入唐學法沙門常曉言。常曉以去承和三年
<lb n="1068c09"/>五月。銜命留學遠期萬里之外。其年漂迴。四
<lb n="1068c10"/>年亦不果渡海。五年六月進發。同年八月到
<lb n="1068c11"/>淮南城廣<note n="1068002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綾＝凌【丙】</note><app n="1068002"><lem>綾</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">凌</rdg></app>&CB00419;安置。孟冬使等入朝。常曉不
<lb n="1068c12"/>得隨使入京。<note n="1068003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">徒＝從【丙】</note><app n="1068003"><lem>徒</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">從</rdg></app>留<note n="1068004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（綾）＋&CB00419;【甲】</note><app n="1068004"><lem>&CB00419;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">綾&CB00419;</rdg></app>&M034294;。空經多日。至于
<lb n="1068c13"/>歲盡&CB00330;命未有<note n="1068005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爰＝受【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1068005"><lem>爰</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">受</rdg></app>。則周遊郡內訪擇師依。幸
<lb n="1068c14"/>遇栖靈寺灌頂阿闍梨法號文&CB03140;和尚。并華
<lb n="1068c15"/>林寺三教講論大德元照座主。其文&CB03140;和尚
<lb n="1068c16"/>則不空三藏弟子。兼<note n="1068006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔惠〕－【甲】</note><app n="1068006"><lem>惠</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>應阿闍梨付法人也。
<lb n="1068c17"/>妙鉤經律深通密藏。法之棟<note n="1068007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梁＝樑【丙】</note><app n="1068007"><lem>梁</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">樑</rdg></app>。國之所歸。
<lb n="1068c18"/>同年臘月。請節度使處分。配住栖靈寺。文&CB03140;
<lb n="1068c19"/>和尚以為師主。始學法儀。兼往花林寺。元照
<lb n="1068c20"/>座主邊問本宗義。并得文書也。然大師尚佛
<lb n="1068c21"/>法之流<note n="1068008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">轉＝傳&M062485;【丙】</note><sic n="1068008" corr="傳" resp="【丙】">轉</sic>。歎生民之可拔。授我以金剛大
<lb n="1068c22"/>法。許我以阿闍梨位也。膝步<note n="1068009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（如）＋知【甲】</note><app n="1068009"><lem>知</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">如知</rdg></app>未知。接足
<lb n="1068c23"/>得<note n="1068010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝未&M062485;【丙】</note><sic n="1068010" corr="未" resp="【丙】">不</sic>得。幸賴國家之大造大師之慈悲。學金
<lb n="1068c24"/>剛<note n="1068011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔海〕－&M062485;【丙】</note><sic n="1068011" corr="＆lac；" resp="【丙】">海</sic>瑜伽。習<note n="1068012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝太【甲】＊</note><app n="1068012"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">太</rdg></app>元帥祕法。斯法也則如來
<lb n="1068c25"/>之肝心。眾生之父母。於國城塹。於人筋脈。是
<lb n="1068c26"/><anchor id="fxT55p1068c01"/>大元帥者。<note n="1068013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">都＋（教）【甲】</note><app n="1068013"><lem>都</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">都教</rdg></app>內不傳於十供奉以外。諸州
<lb n="1068c27"/>無出於節度<note n="1068014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔使〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1068014"><lem>使</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>宅。以表緣其靈驗不可思議
<lb n="1068c28"/>也。諸佛菩薩金剛天等像雖在前來。此像未
<lb n="1068c29"/>曾請來。今則<anchor id="fxT55p1068c02"/>大元帥諸身曼荼羅并諸靈像
<pb ed="T" id="T55.2163.1069a" n="1069a"/>
<lb n="1069a01"/>所要<note n="1069001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">文＝之【丙】</note><app n="1069001"><lem>文</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>書等請來見到。雖云濤波猛<note n="1069002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沷＝沃【丙】</note><app n="1069002"><lem>沷</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">沃</rdg></app>。新
<lb n="1069a02"/>羅賊畔。越<note n="1069003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彼＝波【丙】</note><app n="1069003"><lem>彼</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">波</rdg></app>厄難平達聖境。是則聖力<note n="1069004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069004"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="1069a03"/>所能也。伏惟皇帝陛下。極德如天。佛日高轉。
<lb n="1069a04"/>人之父。佛之化悲群生而濡足。助佛囑而垂
<lb n="1069a05"/>衣。以陛下慈育&CB00283;。祥靈像教希自遠新來。恰
<lb n="1069a06"/>似符契。非聖誰測矣。常曉本謂。果三十年經
<lb n="1069a07"/>歷漢里。求佛法<note n="1069005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">來事＝未事【甲】，來幸【乙】【丙】</note><note n="1069005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來事＝未事【甲】，＝來幸【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069005"><lem>來。事</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">未事</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">來幸</rdg></app>護國家。而緣唐朝不
<lb n="1069a08"/>聽留住。隨使迴歸。竊以一<note n="1069006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喜＝善【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069006"><lem>喜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">善</rdg></app>此法教生而請
<lb n="1069a09"/>來。不任一喜一懼之至。謹附准判官藤原朝
<lb n="1069a10"/>臣貞敏。奉表以聞。并請來法門等目錄一<note n="1069007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">通＝道【甲】</note><app n="1069007"><lem>通</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">道</rdg></app>
<lb n="1069a11"/>且以奉進。輕黷威嚴伏增戰越。常曉誠恐誠
<lb n="1069a12"/>惶謹言</p>
<lb n="1069a13"/><p rend="margin-left:2">承和六年九月二日入唐學法沙門傳燈
<lb n="1069a14"/>大法師位常曉<note place="inline">上表</note></p>
<lb n="1069a15"/><p>入唐學法沙門常曉<note n="1069008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔謹言〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069008"><lem>謹言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p></div1>
<lb n="1069a16"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="上新請來法門并佛像道具事"/><head>上新請來法門并佛像<note n="1069009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道具＝等【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069009"><lem>道具</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">等</rdg></app>事</head>
<lb n="1069a17"/><list><item><title>百論疏</title>一部三卷<note place="inline">元康法師造</note></item>
<lb n="1069a18"/><item><title>三論玄樞</title>一部二卷<note place="inline">元康法師造</note></item>
<lb n="1069a19"/><item><title>中論三十六門勢疏一卷</title><note place="inline">元康法師造</note></item>
<lb n="1069a20"/><item><title>百論疏略記</title>一部二卷<note place="inline">義持法師造</note></item>
<lb n="1069a21"/><item><title>大佛頂經疏</title>一部六卷<note place="inline">弘抗法師造</note></item>
<lb n="1069a22"/><item><title>大佛頂經<note n="1069010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">玄贊＝略述&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1069010"><lem>玄贊</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">略述</rdg></app></title>一部三卷<note place="inline">惟<note n="1069011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00013;＝慇【甲】</note><app n="1069011"><lem>&CB00013;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">慇</rdg></app>法師造</note>
<lb n="1069a23"/><p rend="margin-left:3">已上六部。依三論宗學頭法師<note n="1069012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丙本冠註曰等下有脫</note>等
<lb n="1069a24"/><note n="1069013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">申＝造【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069013"><lem>申</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">造</rdg></app>求請來</p>
<lb n="1069a25"/><p rend="margin-left:1">凡如來說稱經。菩薩說稱論。人師說<note n="1069014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＝稱【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069014"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">稱</rdg></app>疏
<lb n="1069a26"/>章<note n="1069015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">傳＋（說說）【丙】</note><app n="1069015"><lem>傳</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">傳說說</rdg></app>記等。何以故。唯以佛說經鈍根難解
<lb n="1069a27"/>了。是故菩薩作論釋此。最鈍根之<note n="1069016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">類＝賴【甲】</note><app n="1069016"><lem>類</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">賴</rdg></app>。猶
<lb n="1069a28"/>未得精旨。因而人師作疏章等。細演經論
<pb ed="T" id="T55.2163.1069b" n="1069b"/>
<lb n="1069b01"/>之廣旨。於疏師數般。但邪正異耳。今件疏
<lb n="1069b02"/>等。釋經論尤微微。解義理<note n="1069017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">絕＝極【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069017"><lem>絕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">極</rdg></app>細細。此土
<lb n="1069b03"/>有名彼實未<note n="1069018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">渡＋（論）【甲】</note><app n="1069018"><lem>渡</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">渡論</rdg></app>。諸學<note n="1069019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">徒＝從【丙】</note><app n="1069019"><lem>徒</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">從</rdg></app>等之所疑滯。夫
<lb n="1069b04"/>以。百論者。真諦津途。在前以嘉祥寺疏解
<lb n="1069b05"/>釋文義。有少不足。今以元康法師疏將定
<lb n="1069b06"/>義理也。又空有兩宗論真性理。大佛頂經
<lb n="1069b07"/>以為本模。經本雖先來。其疏未有。於義難
<lb n="1069b08"/>決。如今以此將正空有兩家諍論義。夫一
<lb n="1069b09"/>翼若闕。空行何飛。況乃一乘奧理。義與文
<lb n="1069b10"/><note n="1069020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">違＝遠【甲】【乙】</note><app n="1069020"><lem>違</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">遠</rdg></app>。不假疏記微<note n="1069021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">微＝言【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1069021"><lem>微</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">言</rdg></app>無顯。雖有勞載車。<note n="1069022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">冀＝兼【丙】</note><app n="1069022"><lem>冀</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">兼</rdg></app>
<lb n="1069b11"/>以此俾補乎聖典</p></item>
<lb n="1069b12"/><item><title>四分律羯磨疏</title>一部四卷<note place="inline">道宣律師撰</note>
<lb n="1069b13"/><p rend="margin-left:3">已上一部依律宗學頭法師等之覓來</p>
<lb n="1069b14"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右律羯磨者。眾行手足。佛法壽命也。律家
<lb n="1069b15"/>軌則。雖先備來。少有不全。豈非是文乎。然
<lb n="1069b16"/>則以<note n="1069023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔此〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069023"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>使補其尸羅闕目</p></item>
<lb n="1069b17"/><item><title>釋摩訶衍論疏</title>一部三卷<note place="inline">法敏法師造</note>
<lb n="1069b18"/><p rend="margin-left:3">已上一部。依真言宗傳法阿闍梨等
<lb n="1069b19"/>申求來</p>
<lb n="1069b20"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右<note n="1069024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔釋〕－【丙】</note><app n="1069024"><lem>釋</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>摩訶衍論者。橫釋顯教。&CB00594;括祕藏。
