<lb n="1069c01"/><item><title>維摩經五教義一卷</title><note place="inline">文<note n="1069035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">襲＝龍【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069035"><lem>襲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">龍</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT55p1069c01"/>禪師造</note>
<lb n="1069c02"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右維摩經。窮微盡化。妙絕之稱也。造疏之
<lb n="1069c03"/>人。數般論旨。左右詞&CB00520;。<note n="1069036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB05058;塞＝理蹇【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1069036"><lem>&CB05058;塞</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">理蹇</rdg></app>于是。至開
<lb n="1069c04"/>中液公。大宗蕪蔓真<note n="1069037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔極而…提〕四十四字－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069037" word-count="44"><lem>極而開。今見大唐真
<lb n="1069c05"/>典近代興盛講文學義之類。總此疏等以
<lb n="1069c06"/>為指南。是故每寺講淨名典化度白衣。以
<lb n="1069c07"/>液公疏提</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。撕緇<note n="1069038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">徒＝從【丙】</note><app n="1069038"><lem>徒</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">從</rdg></app>。皆云。雖有<note n="1069039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">論＝諸【甲】</note><app n="1069039"><lem>論</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">諸</rdg></app>師註疏。
<lb n="1069c08"/>惠底未足。乍學此文。法鏡轉明。惠燈益照
<lb n="1069c09"/><note n="1069040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＋（開中道液法師造也）【丙】</note><app n="1069040"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">者開中道液法師造也</rdg></app></p></item>
