<lb n="1069c13"/><item><title>金剛般若經註一卷</title><note place="inline">南嶽王潔<note n="1069045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔註〕－【丙】</note><app n="1069045"><lem>註</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="1069c14"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右疏等。解義妙微行<note n="1069046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耆＝支【甲】，者【乙】【丙】，旨&M062485;【丙】</note><note n="1069046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耆＝支【甲】，＝者【乙】【丙】，＝旨&M062485;【丙】</note><app n="1069046"><lem><sic corr="旨" resp="【丙】">耆</sic></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">支</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">者</rdg></app>那國。此等師疏近
<lb n="1069c15"/>代多興。皆以<note n="1069047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">餘＋（餘）【丙】</note><app n="1069047"><lem>餘</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">餘餘</rdg></app>師<note n="1069048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">制＝製&M062485;【丙】</note><sic n="1069048" corr="製" resp="【丙】">制</sic>為傍。以此等疏為
<lb n="1069c16"/>正。夫以佛教興轉<note n="1069049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">依＝以【丙】</note><app n="1069049"><lem>依</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>能<note n="1069050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宣＋（譜）【甲】【丙】，（譜止）【乙】</note><app n="1069050"><lem>宣</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">宣譜</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">宣譜止</rdg></app>人<note n="1069051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">圻＝&CB14236;【丙】</note><app n="1069051"><lem>圻</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB14236;</rdg></app>古請寄
<lb n="1069c17"/>新實。於經本非所改。於義方用相傳<note n="1069052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">告＝去【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069052"><lem>告</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">去</rdg></app>
<lb n="1069c18"/><note n="1069053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耳＝可【丙】</note><app n="1069053"><lem>耳</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">可</rdg></app></p></item>
