<lb n="1070a07"/><item><title>深沙神記并念誦法一卷</title></item>
<lb n="1070a08"/><item><title>菩提王記一卷</title>
<lb n="1070a09"/><p rend="margin-left:2">所受學諸尊瑜伽灌頂儀軌等如先渡
<lb n="1070a10"/><note n="1070009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">來＝未【丙】</note><app n="1070009"><lem>來</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">未</rdg></app>無殊<note n="1070010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">更＝文【丙】，更＝故&M062485;【丙】</note><app n="1070010"><lem><sic corr="故" resp="【丙】">更</sic></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">文</rdg></app>不注之</p>
<lb n="1070a11"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右顯密之法門。若學得。若未學得。其數不
<lb n="1070a12"/>少。唯<note n="1070011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當代要＝舉未曾【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070011"><lem>當代要</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">舉未曾</rdg></app>有耳。至祕密之宗大體與常
<lb n="1070a13"/>無相違</p></item>
<lb n="1070a14"/><item><title>千光<note n="1070012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="1070012"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>佛像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070a15"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右&M010527;沙如來有&M010527;沙土。隨其本行得稱各
<lb n="1070a16"/>異。唯佛與佛乃所究盡。今千光王佛者。此
<lb n="1070a17"/>是觀音本師。其事<note n="1070013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">灼＝&CB00666;【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070013"><lem>灼</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00666;</rdg></app>然。此像未見。因而
<lb n="1070a18"/>請來如件</p></item>
<lb n="1070a19"/><item><title>水月觀世音菩薩像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070a20"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右大悲之用。化形萬方。觀思眾生。拔苦與
<lb n="1070a21"/>樂。故示像相使物生信。今見唐朝世人。總
<lb n="1070a22"/>以為除災因。天下以為生福緣也。是像此
<lb n="1070a23"/>間未流行。故請來如件</p></item>
<lb n="1070a24"/><item><title><note n="1070014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝太【甲】【丙】＊</note><app n="1070014"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">太</rdg></app>元帥本身將部曼荼羅一鋪</title><note place="inline">總五十餘身</note></item>
<lb n="1070a25"/><item><title><anchor id="fxT55p1070a01"/>大元帥大悲身像一軀</title></item>
<lb n="1070a26"/><item><title><anchor id="fxT55p1070a02"/>大元帥忿怒身像一軀</title></item>
<lb n="1070a27"/><item><title><anchor id="fxT55p1070a03"/>大元帥化身像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070a28"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右<anchor id="fxT55p1070a04"/>大元帥者。如來之教<note n="1070015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝領【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070015"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">領</rdg></app>輪也。佛為含
<lb n="1070a29"/>情作<note n="1070016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">救＝故【丙】</note><app n="1070016"><lem>救</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">故</rdg></app>作護。<note n="1070017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">示＝未【丙】</note><app n="1070017"><lem>示</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">未</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT55p1070a05"/>大元帥形。<note n="1070018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">群＝郡【丙】</note><app n="1070018"><lem>群</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">郡</rdg></app>邪見形
<pb ed="T" id="T55.2163.1070b" n="1070b"/>
<lb n="1070b01"/>頭破七分。眾惡聽名魔<note n="1070019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＝通【甲】【乙】</note><app n="1070019"><lem>道</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">通</rdg></app>塵散。本經云。
<lb n="1070b02"/>佛告阿難。若有國王大臣敬禮誦&CB00057;者。其
<lb n="1070b03"/>人境<note n="1070020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">土＝世【乙】</note><app n="1070020"><lem>土</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">世</rdg></app>。無有惡賊怖難災橫疾疫水旱風
<lb n="1070b04"/>霜。國<anchor id="fxT55p1070b06"/>王倍威德。諸民平<note n="1070021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">秦＝泰【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1070021"><lem>秦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">泰</rdg></app>。若有<note n="1070022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔城〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070022"><lem>城</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>邑
<lb n="1070b05"/>村落持此<note n="1070023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝法【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070023"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>者。莫不蒙利<note n="1070024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等＝益【丙】</note><app n="1070024"><lem>等</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">益</rdg></app>者。又云。若
<lb n="1070b06"/>國土<note n="1070025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">襄＝衰【甲】【乙】，襄禍＝褰&CB02932;【丙】</note><note n="1070025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">襄禍＝褰&CB02932;【丙】，襄＝衰【甲】【乙】</note><app n="1070025"><lem>襄禍</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">褰&CB02932;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">衰禍</rdg></app>。雨<note n="1070026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">澤＝降【丙】</note><app n="1070026"><lem>澤</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">降</rdg></app>不調。以此<anchor id="fxT55p1070b07"/>大元帥&CB00057;安
<lb n="1070b07"/>四<note n="1070027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔城〕－【乙】</note><app n="1070027"><lem>城</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>門上。即得風雨順時。將鎮國<note n="1070028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">土＝上【丙】</note><app n="1070028"><lem>土</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">上</rdg></app>。四
<lb n="1070b08"/>方&CB00444;&CB02584;不起逆心等者。然則如法行。國長
<lb n="1070b09"/><note n="1070029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">存＝在【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070029"><lem>存</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">在</rdg></app>安寧。剎那<note n="1070030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婦＝歸【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1070030"><lem>婦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">歸</rdg></app>人<note n="1070031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">固＝同【甲】【乙】，目【丙】</note><note n="1070031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">固＝同【甲】【乙】，＝目【丙】</note><app n="1070031"><lem>固</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">同</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">目</rdg></app>得十利不可思議
<lb n="1070b10"/>也。大元帥之力。今見唐朝皆依此為治國
<lb n="1070b11"/>之<note n="1070032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寶＝實&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="1070032"><lem>寶</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【甲】">實</rdg></app>。勝&CB02584;之要。<note n="1070033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝見【丙】</note><app n="1070033"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">見</rdg></app>以定自在王菩薩偈
<lb n="1070b12"/>讚曰。我聞元帥名。世間救苦厄。一切<note n="1070034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝厄【甲】</note><app n="1070034"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">厄</rdg></app>
<lb n="1070b13"/>神中。奇特無有<note n="1070035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">比＝此【丙】</note><app n="1070035"><lem>比</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>。種種變化身。而拔眾
<lb n="1070b14"/>生苦。我今聞往昔。<note n="1070036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寶＝實【丙】</note><app n="1070036"><lem>寶</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">實</rdg></app>不可思議</p>
<lb n="1070b15"/><p rend="margin-left:1">此法也。吾朝不多流行。以是略<note n="1070037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">要＝案【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070037"><lem>要</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">案</rdg></app>法儀圖
<lb n="1070b16"/>像請求。息災招福無比<note n="1070038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（此）＋法【丙】</note><app n="1070038"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">此法</rdg></app>。誰非歸依耶</p></item>
<lb n="1070b17"/><item><title>大聖千臂千頭金毘羅童子像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070b18"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右金毘羅童子者。此釋迦之化現也。經云。
<lb n="1070b19"/>佛在歡喜園中為諸眾生說法。是時外道
<lb n="1070b20"/>波旬起諸惡障。令諸眾生受大苦惱。爾時
<lb n="1070b21"/>如來密化自身作金毘羅童子。調伏外道
<lb n="1070b22"/>諸魔。於惡世中饒益眾生。此法也尤鎮國
<lb n="1070b23"/>利物之寶。法力之奇特也不思議。此像并
<lb n="1070b24"/>法儀。持明者所祕。本<note n="1070039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">朝＝猶【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070039"><lem>朝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">猶</rdg></app>未見。請來如件</p></item>
<lb n="1070b25"/><item><title><note n="1070040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大聖〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="1070040"><lem>大聖</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>六童子像一<note n="1070041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軀＝鋪【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070041"><lem>軀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">鋪</rdg></app></title>
<lb n="1070b26"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右六童子者。經云。&CB00278;是過去諸佛之所化
<lb n="1070b27"/>身。為救護一切有情故。若有國土作此法
<lb n="1070b28"/>者。即至而現其身護國利人等者。今見唐
<lb n="1070b29"/>朝世人。多修此法。其力見奧。是靈像此間
<lb n="1070b30"/>未有流行。因而請來。其修行之<note n="1070042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">儀亦甚＝像亦其【乙】，儀示甚【丙】</note><note n="1070042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">儀亦甚＝像亦其【乙】，＝儀示甚【丙】</note><app n="1070042"><lem>儀。亦甚</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">像亦其</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">儀示甚</rdg></app>
<pb ed="T" id="T55.2163.1070c" n="1070c"/>
<lb n="1070c01"/><note n="1070043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（不）＋&CB00520;【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070043"><lem>&CB00520;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">不&CB00520;</rdg></app>略</p></item>
<lb n="1070c02"/><item><title>大聖迦毘羅神王像一<note n="1070044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軀＋（一軀）【丙】</note><app n="1070044"><lem>軀</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">軀一軀</rdg></app></title>
<lb n="1070c03"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右神者。此是如來化身。秦代羅什三藏。昔
<lb n="1070c04"/>周五天感得此神相隨送來。今見唐中皆
<lb n="1070c05"/>貴此神為<note n="1070045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">權＝擁【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070045"><lem>權</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">擁</rdg></app>法護國之憑若有病人稱名
<lb n="1070c06"/>即除。貧窮之人依願必富。靈驗見顯。無有
<lb n="1070c07"/>一人不歸依者。夫佛化從西東流。應時利
<lb n="1070c08"/>物。豈非如來<note n="1070046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">未＝來【甲】【丙】，〔未〕&M062403;－【乙】</note><app n="1070046"><lem>未</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">來</rdg><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>化乎</p></item>
<lb n="1070c09"/><note n="1070047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三光…甚可軌也〕百八十五字－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070047" word-count="185"><lem><item><title>三光天子像一軀</title></item>
<lb n="1070c10"/><item><title>二十八宿像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070c11"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右三光者日月五星名七耀。四四方七星
<lb n="1070c12"/>合二十八宿此土之人唯聞名見光。未知
<lb n="1070c13"/>其形量。今此耀宿之形像尤祕尤密。實有
<lb n="1070c14"/>靈驗。唐國猶不多傳。況乎日朝所未曾見。
<lb n="1070c15"/>但陰陽師等意推作像。以傳式用是不契
<lb n="1070c16"/>當耳。今所請像各有可軌也</p></item>
<lb n="1070c17"/><item><title>聖者菩提王像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070c18"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右菩提王者。大唐山神也。潤州樓山有一
<lb n="1070c19"/>比丘。修練禪業現感此神現形表靈受戒
<lb n="1070c20"/>修道故名菩提王。隨人祈請加護成願。遂
<lb n="1070c21"/>為國鎮人歸也。因茲處處作像人人尊重
<lb n="1070c22"/>親見其事甚可軌也</p></item></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="1070c23"/><item><title>深沙神王像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070c24"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右唐代玄奘三藏遠涉五天感得此神。此
<lb n="1070c25"/>是北方多聞天王化身也。今唐國人總重
<pb ed="T" id="T55.2163.1071a" n="1071a"/>
<lb n="1071a01"/>此神救災成益。其驗現前。無有一人不依
<lb n="1071a02"/>行者。寺&M034294;人家皆在此神。<note n="1071001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自見＝目【乙】</note><app n="1071001"><lem>自見</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">目</rdg></app>靈驗實不
<lb n="1071a03"/>思議。具事如記文。請來如件</p></item>
<lb n="1071a04"/><item><title>菩薩像一軀</title></item>
<lb n="1071a05"/><item><title><note n="1071002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此前行甲乙丙三本俱有七曜二十八宿形像八字</note>護摩爐壇樣一十五種</title>
<lb n="1071a06"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右像唐朝示現。其靈驗奧也。人舉歸。息災
<lb n="1071a07"/>增福無<note n="1071003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＝邊【甲】【乙】</note><app n="1071003"><lem>過</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">邊</rdg></app>此者。具事如記文。請來如件</p>
<lb n="1071a08"/><p rend="margin-left:1">夫至道無言。非言不顯。真際絕形。待形乃
<lb n="1071a09"/>悟。絕形者是真如三寶。示形者其住持三
<lb n="1071a10"/>寶也。如來本願順機變相。大聖慈悲應時
<lb n="1071a11"/>濟物。經云。應以佛身得度者。即現佛身。乃
<lb n="1071a12"/>至八部身得度者。即皆現之而為說法等
<lb n="1071a13"/>也。凡<note n="1071004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔正〕－【丙】</note><app n="1071004"><lem>正</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>法之世。魔伴<note n="1071005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＝立【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071005"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">立</rdg></app>威。<note n="1071006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔所以佛〕－【丙】</note><app n="1071006"><lem>所以佛</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="1071007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">化＝陀&M062485;【甲】【乙】</note><sic n="1071007" corr="陀" resp="【甲】【乙】">化</sic>
<lb n="1071a14"/>多住慈悲。像末之時。邪<note n="1071008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">使＝便【甲】，使競興＝法【丙】</note><note n="1071008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">使競興＝法【丙】，使＝便【甲】</note><app n="1071008"><lem>使競興</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">便競興</rdg></app>。所以如
<lb n="1071a15"/>來。多形忿怒。佛力如是。實鎮國利人之寶
<lb n="1071a16"/>也。受持頂戴。福利無極。外以摧魔軍。內以
<lb n="1071a17"/>調伏煩惱。諸佛智悲如此</p></item></list></div1>
