<lb n="1071a24"/><item><title>多羅梵夾一口</title></item>
<lb n="1071a25"/><item><title>金剛<note n="1071009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">海＝界【丙】</note><app n="1071009"><lem>海</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">界</rdg></app>三十七尊種子曼荼羅一<note n="1071010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔面〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071010"><lem>面</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></title></item>
<lb n="1071a26"/><item><title><note n="1071011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔君茶…種〕七字－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071011" word-count="7"><lem>君茶壇樣十七種</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></title></item>
<lb n="1071a27"/><item><title><note n="1071012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（西天…條）九字∞（西天…面）六字【甲】</note><note n="1071012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（西天供養白疊巾一條）九字∞（西天檀褥一面）六字【甲】</note><app n="1071012"><lem>西天供養白疊巾一條</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">西天檀褥一面</rdg></app></title></item>
