<lb n="1071a29"/><item><title>傳法阿闍梨授弟子灌頂法二卷</title>
<pb ed="T" id="T55.2163.1071b" n="1071b"/>
<lb n="1071b01"/><p rend="margin-left:1">右道具。&CB00278;栖靈寺阿闍梨之所<note n="1071014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔傳〕－【甲】</note><app n="1071014"><lem>傳</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>付也</p>
<lb n="1071b02"/><p>常曉去承和五年仲夏之月。<note n="1071015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔隨入唐〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071015"><lem>隨入唐</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>判官
<lb n="1071b03"/><note n="1071016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔菅〕－【丙】，菅＝藤&M062485;【丙】</note><app n="1071016"><lem><sic corr="藤" resp="【丙】">菅</sic></lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>原朝臣善主。同上<note n="1071017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">第四舶發＝弟【丙】</note><app n="1071017"><lem>第四舶發</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">弟</rdg></app><note n="1071018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">赴＝起【丙】</note><app n="1071018"><lem>赴</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">起</rdg></app><note n="1071019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尸＝支【甲】</note><app n="1071019"><lem>尸</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">支</rdg></app>那。
<lb n="1071b04"/>其<note n="1071020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔年〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071020"><lem>年</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>六月到揚州著岸。八月下<note n="1071021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">旬＝句【丙】</note><app n="1071021"><lem>旬</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">句</rdg></app>到淮南
<lb n="1071b05"/>大都督府廣<note n="1071022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綾＝凌【丙】</note><app n="1071022"><lem>綾</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">凌</rdg></app>&CB00419;安置。同年十二月住栖靈
<lb n="1071b06"/>寺大悲持念院。隨同寺灌頂阿闍梨文&CB03140;和
<lb n="1071b07"/>尚。并華林寺三教講論大德元照座主。顯密
<lb n="1071b08"/>兩法頗以兼習。六年正月四日設<note n="1071023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝一【丙】</note><app n="1071023"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">一</rdg></app><note n="1071024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">百＝日【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071024"><lem>百</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">日</rdg></app>僧
<lb n="1071b09"/>齋。普供四眾。於此日諸寺大德綱維&CB00278;臨齋
<lb n="1071b10"/>會應供隨喜。常曉夜就師邊受學瑜伽。<note n="1071025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">晝＝盡【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1071025"><lem>晝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">盡</rdg></app>周
<lb n="1071b11"/>諸寺<note n="1071026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">覓＝不見【丙】</note><app n="1071026"><lem>覓</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">不見</rdg></app><note n="1071027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">問＝向【丙】</note><app n="1071027"><lem>問</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">向</rdg></app>法門。則喚<note n="1071028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔即〕－&M062485;【丙】</note><sic n="1071028" corr="＆lac；" resp="【丙】">即</sic>供奉李<note n="1071029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">全＝金【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071029"><lem>全</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">金</rdg></app>等圖
<lb n="1071b12"/>繪<anchor id="fxT55p1071b01"/>大元帥<note n="1071030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">將＝大&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1071030"><lem>將</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">大</rdg></app>部曼荼羅等諸尊像。并寫文
<lb n="1071b13"/>書。漸有次第。二月十九日受傳法阿闍梨位
<lb n="1071b14"/>灌頂。於此日設大齋普供大眾。留後判官藤
<lb n="1071b15"/>原朝臣貞敏。別<note n="1071031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔請丹墀〕－【丙】</note><app n="1071031"><lem>請丹墀</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>真人高主知乘安墀
<lb n="1071b16"/>宿禰<note n="1071032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔良棟〕－【丙】</note><app n="1071032"><lem>良棟</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>等。<note n="1071033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">同＝聞【丙】</note><app n="1071033"><lem>同</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">聞</rdg></app>臨道場。拋花定本尊。受五
<lb n="1071b17"/>智灌頂。二十一日准&CB00330;離州&CB00230;赴本朝。常曉
<lb n="1071b18"/>本業三論之枝。兼真言之條。而才能不聞。言
<lb n="1071b19"/>無取。逢時<note n="1071034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之人＝乏人【甲】，乏入【乙】</note><note n="1071034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之人＝乏人【甲】，＝乏入【乙】</note><app n="1071034"><lem>之人</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">乏人</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">乏入</rdg></app><note n="1071035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">簉＝選&M062485;【丙】</note><sic n="1071035" corr="選" resp="【丙】">簉</sic>留學<note n="1071036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">員＝真【乙】，貞【丙】</note><note n="1071036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">員＝真【乙】，＝貞【丙】</note><app n="1071036"><lem>員</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">真</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">貞</rdg></app>限以三十年。尋
<lb n="1071b20"/>以一乘。任重人<note n="1071037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弱＝溺【丙】</note><app n="1071037"><lem>弱</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">溺</rdg></app>。夙夜懃<note n="1071038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愿＝慇【甲】</note><app n="1071038"><lem>愿</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">慇</rdg></app>。雖然國命難
<lb n="1071b21"/>乖<note n="1071039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忘＝忌【丙】</note><app n="1071039"><lem>忘</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">忌</rdg></app><note n="1071040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">親＝視【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071040"><lem>親</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">視</rdg></app>萬里住<note n="1071041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝止【丙】</note><app n="1071041"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">止</rdg></app>遠境。且頗受學顯密兩
<lb n="1071b22"/>道。比未見及太<note n="1071042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">知＝和【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071042"><lem>知</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">和</rdg></app>有&CB00330;不聽<note n="1071043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">留＝&CB08619;【丙】</note><app n="1071043"><lem>留</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&CB08619;</rdg></app>住。<note n="1071044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（因）＋而【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1071044"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">因而</rdg></app>隨使
<lb n="1071b23"/>&CB00230;迴。少間所成<note n="1071045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝些些【甲】【乙】，此＋（此）【丙】</note><app n="1071045"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">些些</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">此此</rdg></app>法儀注顯如件</p>
<lb n="1071b24"/><p rend="margin-left:1">承和六年九月五日</p>
<lb n="1071b25"/><p rend="margin-left:3">入唐學法沙門傳燈大法師位常曉上</p></item></list></div1>
